{"tid":2405436,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【原來是趙同志】中国「戰狼」趙立堅按讚 \"同志色情網站\"","createTime":"2021-02-12T10:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T11:50:10.000Z","uid":293677,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"08d689c09748ebfafd402ddbaf5b45cc215e4d23","tid":2405436,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">「戰狼」按讚同志色情網站 趙立堅又惹議</span><br />\n<br />\n2021/02/12 16:37<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">中國外交部「戰狼」發言人趙立堅</span></span>，去年2月26日上任第二天被抓包推特上關注日本前AV女優蒼井空帳號，甚至還在情色女星的發文下方留下露骨字句。如今他的推特帳號又被曝光<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">關注了同志色情帳號</span></span>，引發熱議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2月11日，趙立堅官方認證的推特帳號@zlj517關注了一個名為「qornograficx」的同志色情帳號，被眼尖的外國YouTuber發現，並上傳影片加以諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n這位YouTuber是化名SerpentZA的斯特澤爾（Winston Frederick Sterzel），他曾在中國廣東省深圳生活了14年，經營的「ADVChina」頻道時常探討中國敏感話題引發關注。<br />\n<br />\nSerpentZA在影片中說：「我找到了什麼呢，這個同性戀色情推特帳號的關注者中有戰狼外交官趙立堅，的確有。這太好笑了，這不是捏造，我們現場直播看到的。是的，如果我重新加載界面，上面顯示被趙立堅關注，你點開之後，這就是他，帶有推特藍色認證標籤的，這絕對是他。他就是那個談論澳洲軍人殺害阿富汗兒童的虛假照片的人。是的，他真的是一個品質低下的人，我們應該說他是一個頂級的戰狼外交官。」<br />\n<br />\n這段影片在海外瘋傳，截至目前，中國官方及趙立堅本人還未就此事作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">一位網友在評論這起事件時說，我覺得趙立堅這個戰狼外交官，他好像沒有吸取（前）中國駐英國大使劉曉明的教訓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉曉明去年9月間被網友發現對推特上一則「絲襪足交」的色情推文按讚，引發網友甚至國外政界人物大肆嘲弄。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3438725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3438725&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FM04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=9b554034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3438725&h=59c8d5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3438725</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">中国共產黨或成全球最大&quot;同志&quot;組織</span></span>"},{"pid":"5b841f1a9d71326229b2ceff8955d140b5a9e7e0","tid":2405436,"uid":224533,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"同志，原來你是同志"},{"pid":"ed4e9d3fb2f3c54a2fda166de7b0a46a1947a0d4","tid":2405436,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f0bc2d4a88fe9df538805579c298ced615ac68","tid":2405436,"uid":293677,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5b841f1a9d71326229b2ceff8955d140b5a9e7e0","tid":2405436,"uid":224533,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"同志，原來你是同志"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九千萬都同志"},{"pid":"2a80135f4aed65100f314313d078d4fbab87aa55","tid":2405436,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4f29ccf7f05af6af1e9a7e8117bb3ccd9fec43","tid":2405436,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0f1a92654261ee18ad58bab7353e662ee14193","tid":2405436,"uid":314184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"堅Gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce74acf09636653639b2e4b2a7f28c03c9b13229","tid":2405436,"uid":126508,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":